{"id":35180,"date":"2024-01-17T08:44:00","date_gmt":"2022-06-17T03:14:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=35180"},"modified":"2024-02-08T21:46:10","modified_gmt":"2024-02-08T16:16:10","slug":"storage-bed-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/storage-bed-design\/","title":{"rendered":"Utility Meets Style In These Storage Bed Design Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>Storage bed designs<\/strong> are getting trendier by the day. Explore these styles to redesign your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern homeowners are looking for more practical solutions to deal with everyday interior problems. For example, a bed is mandatory in the bedroom but takes up a lot of space \u2014 instantly reducing the space available for other bedroom essentials like a wardrobe, dressing table and shelves. This is why a piece of thoughtfully-designed, maximum utility furniture is a lifesaver. Innovations with storage bed design are on the rise since wall-mounted Murphy beds aren\u2019t everyone\u2019s favourite. Let\u2019s simplify your hunt for a fabulous storage bed with these design ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"699\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Unique storage bed designs for space-saving\" class=\"wp-image-47926\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-scaled.jpg 699w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-82x300.jpg 82w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-768x2814.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-419x1536.jpg 419w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-559x2048.jpg 559w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/04160004\/unique-storage-bed-designs-150x550.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Swanky Shoe Rack Storage Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We love customising king-size bed designs with storage like we did for this bedroom. While storage drawers are a staple, we included a functional shoe rack in the design too. The addition gives the bed a spectacular twist besides the plush velvet headboard. The multipurpose design enables the footwear to get the protection it needs from dust (and envious glares) without occupying extra space. We\u2019re pleased to say that getting ready and unwinding just got more interesting and hassle-free for this client.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20084848\/swanky-shoe-rack-storage-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Swanky shoe rack storage bed design with a well-designed storage bed is a boon in a bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-35181\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20084848\/swanky-shoe-rack-storage-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20084848\/swanky-shoe-rack-storage-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20084848\/swanky-shoe-rack-storage-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20084848\/swanky-shoe-rack-storage-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A well-designed storage bed is a boon in a bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Bed Design With Storage For Nighty Night<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine a long day at work and getting back to your bed for a good night\u2019s rest. You start with your bedtime routine \u2014 read a few pages of a book, journal your thoughts, play a round of chess, TLC for your skin, and slowly ease into a deep slumber. If you prefer your me-time or us-time by the bed, then custom <strong>cot designs with storage<\/strong> like the one shown here are perfect for you. They keep your routine essentials handy and tidy, making it convenient to place them back too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085139\/king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-for-nighty.jpg\" alt=\"King size bed designs with storage for nighty night with a swanky shoe rack in the storage bed\" class=\"wp-image-35182\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085139\/king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-for-nighty.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085139\/king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-for-nighty-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085139\/king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-for-nighty-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085139\/king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-for-nighty-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Set up a swanky shoe rack in the storage bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Single Bed Design With Storage For Children<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The USP of modular furniture is that there\u2019s no limit to how something can be customised. Even a single bed for a child can be built with storage space. Also, when it\u2019s for children, the storage handles are designed child-friendly. Stuffed toys, favourite board games, storybooks, piggy bank \u2014 everything can be tucked away neatly in the storage compartments provided. The pop of yellow gives it a playful vibe and matches the rest of the room \u2014 which has also been designed for optimal utility with short shelves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085715\/modern-bed-design-with-storage-for-children.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bed design with storage for Child-friendly storage beds in playful shades\" class=\"wp-image-35183\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085715\/modern-bed-design-with-storage-for-children.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085715\/modern-bed-design-with-storage-for-children-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085715\/modern-bed-design-with-storage-for-children-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20085715\/modern-bed-design-with-storage-for-children-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Child-friendly storage beds in playful shades<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Enjoy Extra Storage With A Hydraulic Bed&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Some people don\u2019t like scanning too many shelves or opening multiple drawers to reach for that one item. For such folks, hydraulic <strong>cot designs with storage<\/strong> are the best form of space-saving, multipurpose furniture. The lift-up frame allows easy scanning and access to hidden compartments. The frame also acts as the door to the concealed cupboard. This setup is also convenient for those who like their things to be kept away from plain sight, especially in a compact room. Don\u2019t you agree that the custom headboard and the aesthetic timepiece also add to the room\u2019s elegance? The right mix of multipurpose furniture and decor can do that!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090018\/enjoy-extra-storage-with-a-hydraulic-double-bed-design-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Enjoy extra storage with a hydraulic double bed design with storage\" class=\"wp-image-35184\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090018\/enjoy-extra-storage-with-a-hydraulic-double-bed-design-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090018\/enjoy-extra-storage-with-a-hydraulic-double-bed-design-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090018\/enjoy-extra-storage-with-a-hydraulic-double-bed-design-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090018\/enjoy-extra-storage-with-a-hydraulic-double-bed-design-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A hydraulic bed offers convenience and utility<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wooden Bed Design With Storage For Small Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Even if you aren\u2019t exactly Marie Kondo-ing your home, there\u2019s some joy in organising things into different compartments to whatever extent you can. A plywood bed with multiple easy-to-use drawers offers more space for efficient organisation. The cost-effective veneer finish gives it the natural wood look. This kind of <strong>plywood bed design with storage<\/strong> is useful in smaller rooms such as the guest room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090206\/wooden-bed-design-with-storage-for-small-spaces-1.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden bed design with storage for small spaces with multiple easy-to-use drawers offers more space \" class=\"wp-image-35186\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090206\/wooden-bed-design-with-storage-for-small-spaces-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090206\/wooden-bed-design-with-storage-for-small-spaces-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090206\/wooden-bed-design-with-storage-for-small-spaces-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090206\/wooden-bed-design-with-storage-for-small-spaces-1-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Wooden storage bed for small spaces <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mystery Storage Bed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We love designing multifunctional furniture. We love it further when we get to be playful with it. The storage bed we delivered for this client\u2019s bedroom doesn\u2019t just contain the standard drawer setup. It also elegantly conceals a functional bookshelf. And the custom headboard acts as a rack for splendid souvenirs or everyday use articles. That\u2019s one bed performing many roles, thus saving plenty of floor space!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090424\/a-mystery-storage-bed-design-1.jpg\" alt=\"A bookshelf cum storage bed for a mystery trail where custom headboard acts as a rack for splendid souvenirs\" class=\"wp-image-35188\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090424\/a-mystery-storage-bed-design-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090424\/a-mystery-storage-bed-design-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090424\/a-mystery-storage-bed-design-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090424\/a-mystery-storage-bed-design-1-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A bookshelf cum storage bed for a mystery trail<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The All-Rounder Of Storage Beds<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>How wonderful would it be to have a bed with all kinds of storage! In other words, how about a <strong>double bed design with storage<\/strong> as in this bedroom? This design is the best of both worlds as it blends a <strong>hydraulic <\/strong>bed<em> <\/em>and a <strong>conventional <\/strong>storage bed with pull-out drawers. Both aspects of storage can be used simultaneously resulting in maximum utility without additional space. Don\u2019t you just love the perks of modular furniture?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090715\/the-all-rounder-of-king-size-bed-designs-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"The all-rounder of king size bed designs with storage with Blended hydraulic and conventional storage \" class=\"wp-image-35189\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090715\/the-all-rounder-of-king-size-bed-designs-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090715\/the-all-rounder-of-king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090715\/the-all-rounder-of-king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090715\/the-all-rounder-of-king-size-bed-designs-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blended hydraulic and conventional storage bed <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019d say it\u2019s fair to declare that a bed is no longer a place for just a good night\u2019s rest. It has to offer more in terms of features for organising the room. And when it comes to space-efficient beds, there\u2019s more than just storage beds. If you\u2019d like to know about such space-saver beds, do check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/space-saving-bed-for-small-rooms\/\">this <\/a>blog. But for now, we\u2019ve come to the end of this list of storage bed design ideas. Well, what\u2019s your verdict on them? Eager to get one customised for your bedroom? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Here<\/a> you go to book your appointment with our expert, design-savvy team.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about storage bed design ideas, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wall-mounted-murphy-bed-designs\/\">wall-mounted murphy bed designs<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" cl